transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Hi, my name is Rich Schneiderite. I have a prescription for you guys. I just contacted

Speaker 1: the other place and they told me how to call you. I'm trying to cancel the prescription.

Speaker 2: Sure. Can I have your phone number so I can fill up your account?

Speaker 1: Sure. 732-715-0931.

Speaker 2: Thank you, Richard. Can you just confirm your date of birth?

Speaker 1: August 26, 62.

Speaker 2: Thank you so much. Is he your VIP status customer? And how's the medication working out for you?

Speaker 1: Not that good. That's why I'm canceling it.

Speaker 2: Yeah, that's what I'm asking. It looks like the pharmacy made an error and you just received

Speaker 1: generic Viagra. You did not receive the AGV. Do you happen to have them on you by any chance?

Speaker 2: No, I don't.

Speaker 1: Okay. Give me a second. I'm going to get you out a replacement and then I'm going to tell you how

Speaker 2: you can confirm you received the correct medication.

Speaker 1: I don't need a replacement. I just want to cancel it totally.

Speaker 2: All right. No problem. I went ahead and closed out your account. You're all set.

Speaker 1: All right. Thank you very much.

Speaker 2: No problem.

Speaker 1: Have a great day.

Speaker 2: You too. Thanks.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.
